gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

Daily I go to the river, with friends taking song; 
Saintly songs make Shyamalo, extremely colorful play and I am satisfied.

Here is the translation:

Arrived seated opposite, lovely waves dance; 
Beautiful group of saints, that one will not go silent again.

Here is the translation:

Filled lamp there shines very; 
White island seems same, beauty that is so much.

This is the translation:

This is Asura's defeat, Shyamalioj rejoiced becoming;
Behold, behold the slave, mercy did do mercy.

After that, the saint went; 
From there, he took leave in haste; 
He saw Dega's vision, came with joy and pity.
